Add resource state tags on host, VM, cluster, and host storage metrics so capacity-planning queries can scope to only healthy, available resources:

  * `ntnx_maintenance_state` and `ntnx_connection_state` on host metrics
  * `ntnx_power_state` on VM metrics
  * `ntnx_operation_mode` on cluster metrics
  * `ntnx_disk_status` on host storage metrics
